---
---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="overline">Independent Builder</p>
    <h1>
      Building an ecosystem<br />
      <span class="accent">where every tool serves every other.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="body-text">
      Backend developer from Vietnam with 7 years shipping Node.js and AWS at scale.<br class="br-desktop" />
      Now building an indie game dev ecosystem — tools, games, and content pipelines<br class="br-desktop" />
      where every piece feeds the others. Also available for select freelance work.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">See what I'm building →</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">Work with me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem);
  }

  .overline {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .body-text {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.15rem);
    max-width: 58ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .br-desktop { display: none; }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .br-desktop { display: block; }
  }
</style>
